      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <!-- FAQ 1 -->
        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-lg text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
            How often should I get a facial?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-neutral-600">For optimal results, we recommend getting a facial every 4-6 weeks to maintain healthy, glowing skin and address specific concerns.</p>
        </details>

        <!-- FAQ 2 -->
        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-lg text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
            What should I expect during my first visit?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-neutral-600">Your first visit includes a skin consultation to assess your skin type and concerns, followed by a customized treatment plan tailored to your needs.</p>
        </details>

        <!-- FAQ 3 -->
        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-lg text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
            Is there any downtime after treatments?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-neutral-600">Most treatments have little to no downtime. Chemical peels may cause slight redness for 1-2 days. We'll provide detailed aftercare instructions for each service.</p>
        </details>

        <!-- FAQ 4 -->
        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-lg text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
            Can I wear makeup after a facial?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-neutral-600">We recommend avoiding makeup for at least 6-8 hours after your facial to allow your skin to fully absorb the treatment benefits.</p>
        </details>

        <!-- FAQ 5 -->
        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-lg text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
            What's the difference between a chemical peel and microdermabrasion?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-neutral-600">Chemical peels use acids to exfoliate and resurface skin, while microdermabrasion physically removes dead skin cells. Both improve texture, but peels penetrate deeper for more dramatic results.</p>
        </details>

        <!-- FAQ 6 -->
        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-lg text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
            Do you offer consultations?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-neutral-600">Yes! We offer free consultations to discuss your skincare goals and recommend the best treatment plan for your specific needs.</p>
        </details>

        <!-- FAQ 7 -->
        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-lg text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
            What is your cancellation policy?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-neutral-600">We require 24-hour notice for cancellations or rescheduling. Late cancellations may be subject to a fee. Please contact us as soon as possible if you need to change your appointment.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
